node.text:
🌿 OMNI KITCHEN 🌿
Sharing with y’all a healthier alternative for food deliveries this period - If you are taking this time to eat clean, you can head over to @omnikitchen.sg! These healthier bentos are reasonably priced, from $7.90 onwards. Recommend y’all to get the “Chicken Winner”!! With “SHERMAINEXOMNI”, you can get an additional 10% off their current prices, making it even more affordable. Valid for takeaways and deliveries! Swipe to see the special promo for May + ordering details 😋😋😋 #Omnikitchen
The mushrooms look so succulent 🤤 generous portions too!
